<p class="hamesh">١ semple; influences of grographic environment, pP. ٤٨٦, ٤٨٨.<br>٢ ibid,. P. ٤٩٠<br>٣ ency. of islam; art. arabia, P. ٣٧٥; &amp; semlpe; influences of geographic environment, P. ٥٠٠.<br>٤ انظر الفصل الثامن من الباب الخامس من الكتاب الأول من المقدمة/ ٣٩٤.<br>٥ the ency. of islam; art. arabia, P. ٣٧٥.</p> </div>